# OpenClaw .env example
#
# Canonical secret location (NEVER COMMIT):
#   ~/.openclaw/.env  — host-side, used by docker-compose and launchd/systemd.
# Copy this file there and fill real values. Keep secrets out of Git.
#
# Fallback (repo-adjacent): .env or .env.local.runtime in this directory.
# Env-source precedence (highest -> lowest): process env, ~/.openclaw/.env,
# .env.local.runtime, .env, then openclaw.json `env` block.
# Existing non-empty process env vars are not overridden by dotenv/config env loading.
# Note: direct config keys (for example `gateway.auth.token` or channel tokens in openclaw.json)
# are resolved separately from env loading and often take precedence over env fallbacks.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Gateway auth + paths
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Recommended if the gateway binds beyond loopback.
OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=change-me-to-a-long-random-token
# Example generator: openssl rand -hex 32

# Optional alternative auth mode (use token OR password).
# OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PASSWORD=change-me-to-a-strong-password

# Optional path overrides (defaults shown for reference).
# OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=~/.openclaw
# OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=~/.openclaw/openclaw.json
# OPENCLAW_HOME=~

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Operator transport parity (optional local -> K8s wiring)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Canonical internal control boundary inside Tonya. Legacy Angela env names still
# work, but new parity wiring should prefer the INTERNAL_CONTROL names.
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_INTERNAL_CONTROL_URL=http://tonya.agents.svc.cluster.local:18789
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_INTERNAL_CONTROL_SHARED_SECRET=replace-me
#
# Canonical local -> K8s project-ops boundary. Local should talk to Tonya's
# control plane, and Tonya forwards to the single in-cluster Deb service.
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_CONTROL_PLANE_URL=https://tonya.aegean-bull.ts.net
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_CONTROL_PLANE_SHARED_SECRET=replace-me
#
# Direct Deb envs are still supported as a fallback, but they are no longer the
# preferred local parity path because Deb remains private inside K8s.
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_DEB_URL=http://deb.agents.svc.cluster.local:3010
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_DEB_SHARED_SECRET=replace-me
#
# Explicit worker plane for 2Tony dispatches when needed.
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_2TONY_URL=http://two-tony.agents.svc.cluster.local:3009
# OPENCLAW_OPERATOR_2TONY_SHARED_SECRET=replace-me

# Optional: import missing keys from your login shell profile.
# OPENCLAW_LOAD_SHELL_ENV=1
# OPENCLAW_SHELL_ENV_TIMEOUT_MS=15000

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Model provider API keys (set at least one)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=...
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
# OPENCLAW_LIVE_OPENAI_KEY=sk-...
# OPENCLAW_LIVE_ANTHROPIC_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENCLAW_LIVE_GEMINI_KEY=...
# OPENAI_API_KEY_1=...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY_1=...
# GEMINI_API_KEY_1=...
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=...
# OPENAI_API_KEYS=sk-1,sk-2
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEYS=sk-ant-1,sk-ant-2
# GEMINI_API_KEYS=key-1,key-2

# Optional additional providers
# ZAI_API_KEY=...
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=...
# MINIMAX_API_KEY=...
# SYNTHETIC_API_KEY=...

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Channels (only set what you enable)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABCDEF...
# DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=...
# SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-...
# SLACK_APP_TOKEN=xapp-...

# Optional channel env fallbacks
# MATTERMOST_BOT_TOKEN=...
# MATTERMOST_URL=https://chat.example.com
# ZALO_BOT_TOKEN=...
# OPENCLAW_TWITCH_ACCESS_TOKEN=oauth:...

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Tools + voice/media (optional)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# BRAVE_API_KEY=...
# PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=pplx-...
# FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=...

# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=...
# XI_API_KEY=...  # alias for ElevenLabs
# DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=...
